{"tid":640111,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"咁樣算唔算有潔癖","createTime":"2018-04-24T04:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T05:06:05.000Z","uid":4176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16f5325cc2723d8ab2ec7e01aa6432bfc081375d","tid":640111,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:45:45.000Z","msg":"每次掂塊面之前都一定要用梘液洗手<br />\n掂到任何唔係自己嘅野都會覺得好污糟<br />\n就算係屋企啲野都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次嚴重到樓上裝修緊 我要閂窗 隻手伸咗岀窗外覺得成手灰塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岀街由閂門嗰刻起就唔會再亂咁掂野<br />\n<br />\n但又可以忍到個書枱啲notes勁亂<br />\n有時候床鋪都唔會換得好密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底咁樣係唔係潔癖"},{"pid":"0bcf541d5b2ef94198742f6c8b4d1fa7bc424cad","tid":640111,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7e64d044ae11e4dadfe5eb4b3141df580920f76","tid":640111,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"算"},{"pid":"b4a3cb8e80f1ecbfd7d87f903a3fbe0870bf9efc","tid":640111,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"強逼症"},{"pid":"22510e9caafed2e02ba123c2ee0ea45f6803ff68","tid":640111,"uid":4176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3cb8e80f1ecbfd7d87f903a3fbe0870bf9efc","tid":640111,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"強逼症"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"點分強迫症同潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddac40698bdf83c1c11f8ff83e42f8880029e35e","tid":640111,"uid":4176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"雖然好鍾意用梘液洗手 但又覺得街外廁所梘液放咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0811fefed2f9f95827d29c55a0826f6c91ee327b","tid":640111,"uid":100230